additionalInfo.description:
Formats a 10 digit number into the standard 999 999 9999 standard format for NHS Numbers. All punctuation is removed. An alpha characters will be left as is. 
If the remaining characters are not a 10 digit number, then the number will not be standardized and the original number will be output.

Tags: Contact, Standardize, GBR,UK, Integrity/Conformity
Removes all punctuation symbols and character spaces from an input field, and returns the remaining digits and letters.
